A '''Corellian pirate''' was part of the group that escorted [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba the Hutt]] to [[Docking Bay 94/Legends|Docking Bay 94]] in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] to confront [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. Minutes prior he had been drinking in [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina]], along with [[Boelo]] and [[Gela Yeens]].

==Behind the scenes==
One of three "Corellian pirates",<ref name="SWC">''[[Star Wars Chronicles]]'' (p. 86)</ref> this character, played by [[Ron Tarr]], appeared in a scene which was originally deleted from [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] but was included in the [[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|Special Edition]] release of the film. However, he has always been present inside the cantina.<ref name="SWCA">{{SW|url=news/swca-secrets-of-the-mos-eisley-cantina-panel-liveblog|text=SWCA: Secrets of the Mos Eisley Cantina Panel Liveblog|nolive=1}}</ref>

